attributes.action: Open a nightclub/Bar in the town of Woking Surrey!
attributes.additional_details: It will bring in more income for the ‘in debt’ town of Woking
attributes.background: Get somebody or get the permissions to open up a nightclub in Woking since the closure of the others there is now no night life in the town of Woking

rejection.details:
We can only accept petitions about things the Government or Parliament are directly responsible for. 
 
Decisions about opening bars and nightclubs are a matter for individual businesses and local authorities, not the UK Government or Parliament.
